snippet.title: F.E.A.R. Extraction Point - Trailer
snippet.description: A trailer for F.E.A.R. Extraction Point, the expansion pack for the PC game F.E.A.R.. Soon to be released along with Perseus Mandate in a package known as F.E.A.R. Files for the Xbox 360.
